{"tid":2127204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】新鴻基觀塘地盤爆疫 續無罩施工拒停 工人怕傳染家人自費住酒店","createTime":"2020-07-27T08:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T01:05:41.000Z","uid":2719,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"662414a96acfb65884688f3c1d550be07f5537b4","tid":2127204,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:06:30.000Z","msg":"本港武肺疫情未有遏止迹象，各行各業陸續有打工仔「中招」。據了解，新鴻基地產在觀塘巧明街的地盤，本月先後有兩名地盤工人確診染疫，有工人透露，地盤獲悉有人確診後只作簡單消毒。而連日天氣酷熱，大部份工友都「無罩」開工，加上地盤環境難以保持1.5米社交距離，擔心病毒在地盤爆發，盼政府及發展商為地盤工人安排深喉唾液測試。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200727/2MVBNZD3E4N2MQY4NAKJI5HHFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2F2MVBNZD3E4N2MQY4NAKJI5HHFM%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=162667b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2F2MVBNZD3E4N2MQY4NAKJI5HHFM%2F&h=8b1b1535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200727/2MVBNZD3E4N2MQY4NAKJI5HHFM/</a>"},{"pid":"512e4d8ce566bbe8e4d82596abeaf900928bd554","tid":2127204,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:12:41.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"965be24a030659a7e1dd85ece4a321040997ecf0","tid":2127204,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:22:28.000Z","msg":"唔好遲起貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084bf8907235211da4030e39a5439b45e0ae40ee","tid":2127204,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"地盤佬最高危"},{"pid":"20c27c475f25b715269444d690c689168408c0d4","tid":2127204,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:27:46.000Z","msg":"香港地做藍領不嬲折墮"},{"pid":"646dbcd5ed29318defe9f7511d8ca1b93830ebf4","tid":2127204,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,